sequenceDiagram
    autonumber
    actor Student
    participant ESB as ESB Gateway
    participant Finance as Finance Service
    participant Academic as Academic Service
    participant RabbitMQ as Message Broker
    participant Notif as Notification Service

    Student->>ESB: POST /api/v1/academic/enrollments
    activate ESB
    
    Note over ESB: Step 1: Check Finance (Prerequisite)
    ESB->>Finance: GET /finance/invoices?status=unpaid
    activate Finance
    Finance-->>ESB: [] (No unpaid invoices)
    deactivate Finance
    
    Note over ESB: Step 2: Create Enrollment
    ESB->>Academic: POST /academic/enrollments
    activate Academic
    Academic-->>ESB: 201 Created (Enrollment Data)
    deactivate Academic
    
    Note over ESB: Step 3: Async Notification
    ESB-)RabbitMQ: Publish ENROLLMENT_CONFIRMED message
    
    ESB-->>Student: 201 Created (Success)
    deactivate ESB
    
    Note over RabbitMQ,Notif: Asynchronous Process
    RabbitMQ-)Notif: Consume message
    activate Notif
    Notif->>Notif: Send Email to Student
    deactivate Notif
